import React from 'react';
import { Card, CardHeader, CardContent, Typography, Grid, Avatar } from '@mui/material';
import { makeStyles } from '@mui/styles';
import { AccountCircle, Email, Business, LocationOn, Phone, BusinessCenter, CreditCard, People } from '@mui/icons-material';
import profile from './profile.png'; // Importing the profile image

const useStyles = makeStyles((theme) => ({
  card: {
    width: '100%',
    maxWidth: '800px',
    margin: 'auto',
    marginTop: theme.spacing(4),
    backgroundColor: '#f5f5f5', // Light gray background
    borderRadius: '40px', // Rounded corners
    boxShadow: '0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)', // Light shadow effect
    padding: theme.spacing(5), // Add padding
    border: '1px solid #e0e0e0', // Light gray border
  },
  header: {
    backgroundColor: '#d7a022', // Yellow header background
    color: '#fff', // White header text
    borderRadius: '10px 10px 0 0', // Rounded top corners
    padding: theme.spacing(2), // Add padding
    textAlign: 'center', // Center align text
  },
  headerTitle: {
    fontSize: '20px', // Decreased header font size
    fontFamily: 'Arial, sans-serif', // Header font family
    fontWeight: 'bold', // Bold header text
    marginBottom: theme.spacing(1), // Add some margin at the bottom
  },
  content: {
    padding: theme.spacing(4), // Add padding
  },
  typography: {
    fontFamily: 'Arial, sans-serif', // Font family for content
    color: '#333333', // Dark text color
    fontSize: '1.2rem', // Decreased font size for content
    display: 'flex',
    alignItems: 'center', // Center icon and text vertically
    marginBottom: theme.spacing(2), // Add some margin at the bottom
  },
  icon: {
    marginRight: theme.spacing(1), // Add space between icon and text
    color: '#d7a022', // Yellow icon color
  },
  avatar: {
    width: theme.spacing(8),
    height: theme.spacing(8),
    marginRight: theme.spacing(2),
  },
}));

const UserProfileCard = () => {
  const classes = useStyles();

  return (
    <Card className={classes.card}>
      <CardHeader
        className={classes.header}
        title={<Typography variant="h2" className={classes.headerTitle}>Basic Information</Typography>}
      />
      <CardContent className={classes.content}>
        <Grid container spacing={2}>
          <Grid item xs={3}>
            <Avatar alt="Profile Picture" src={profile} className={classes.avatar} />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={9}>
            <Typography variant="body1" className={classes.typography}>
              <AccountCircle className={classes.icon} />
              Name: 
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body1" className={classes.typography}>
              <Email className={classes.icon} />
              Email: 
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body1" className={classes.typography}>
              <Phone className={classes.icon} />
              Phone Number: +1234567890
            </Typography>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </CardContent>
      <CardHeader
        className={classes.header}
        title={<Typography variant="h2" className={classes.headerTitle}>Business Information</Typography>}
      />
      <CardContent className={classes.content}>
        <Grid container spacing={2}>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <Typography variant="body1" className={classes.typography}>
              <BusinessCenter className={classes.icon} />
              Company: ABC Corporation
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body1" className={classes.typography}>
              <Business className={classes.icon} />
              Business Type: Retail
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body1" className={classes.typography}>
              <LocationOn className={classes.icon} />
              Business Branches: 5
            </Typography>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <Typography variant="body1" className={classes.typography}>
              <People className={classes.icon} />
              Number of Employees: 20
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body1" className={classes.typography}>
              <CreditCard className={classes.icon} />
              Expected Credit: 
            </Typography>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
  );
};

export default UserProfileCard;
